# TASK_PACKET

Task ID
CRUSHR-VERIFY-UI-01

Title
Professional verification report presentation for `crushr-extract --verify`

Role
BUILDER

Objective
Implement a deterministic, operator-grade verification report presentation for `crushr-extract --verify` that is immediately readable in terminal use, defensible in screenshots/reports, and aligned with the canonical verification model and trust semantics already established by prior hardening work.

This packet exists because the codebase may now be structurally truthful, but the verification surface still needs to present that truth in a form that security, forensic, legal, and incident-response users can understand quickly and trust.

This is a presentation-contract packet.
It is not a semantics-redesign packet.

